# Assets Current Property Amount

## identifier
de8947

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of property held by the reporting party as at the relevant date, that are classified as current assets, as determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.CurrentProperty.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
